---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Kinevra - SAP Integration Experts" description="Learn about Kinevra's mission to transform enterprises through expert SAP integration and Business Technology Platform solutions.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="blur-bg blur-bg-1"></div>
    <div class="blur-bg blur-bg-2"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero-content">
        <h1 class="gradient-text animate-slide-up">About Kinevra</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
          Pioneering the future of enterprise integration with cutting-edge SAP solutions
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <div class="content-block animate-slide-up">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
              At Kinevra, we believe in the transformative power of intelligent integration. Our mission is to empower enterprises 
              with seamless SAP solutions that drive innovation, efficiency, and growth. We specialize in bridging the gap between 
              traditional enterprise systems and modern cloud technologies.
            </p>
            <p>
              Founded with a vision to simplify complex SAP landscapes, Kinevra brings deep technical expertise and a personalized 
              approach to every engagement. We understand that each business is unique, and we tailor our solutions to meet your 
              specific challenges and objectives.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block animate-slide-up">
            <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üéØ</div>
                <h3>Focused Expertise</h3>
                <p>Specialized exclusively in SAP integration and BTP, ensuring deep knowledge and best practices.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">‚ö°</div>
                <h3>Agile Delivery</h3>
                <p>Quick turnaround times with flexible engagement models that adapt to your project needs.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">ü§ù</div>
                <h3>Personal Touch</h3>
                <p>Direct communication and dedicated attention to ensure your project's success.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">üîÆ</div>
                <h3>Future Ready</h3>
                <p>Stay ahead with modern architectures and emerging technologies in the SAP ecosystem.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block animate-slide-up">
            <h2>Our Approach</h2>
            <p>
              We believe in building lasting partnerships with our clients. Our approach combines technical excellence with 
              strategic thinking to deliver solutions that not only solve immediate challenges but also position your business 
              for future success.
            </p>
            <div class="approach-steps">
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Understand</h4>
                  <p>Deep dive into your business processes and technical landscape</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Design</h4>
                  <p>Architect solutions that align with your strategic objectives</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Implement</h4>
                  <p>Execute with precision using industry best practices</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Support</h4>
                  <p>Provide ongoing optimization and support for continuous improvement</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card glass-card animate-slide-in">
            <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
            <ul class="facts-list">
              <li><strong>Founded:</strong> 2024</li>
              <li><strong>Focus:</strong> SAP & BTP</li>
              <li><strong>Approach:</strong> Boutique Consultancy</li>
              <li><strong>Support:</strong> 24/7 Available</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card glass-card animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
            <h3>Core Values</h3>
            <ul class="values-list">
              <li>Excellence in Execution</li>
              <li>Client-First Mindset</li>
              <li>Continuous Innovation</li>
              <li>Transparent Communication</li>
              <li>Sustainable Solutions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card glass-card animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <h3>Let's Connect</h3>
            <p>Ready to transform your SAP landscape?</p>
            <a href="mailto:daniel@kinevra.com" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content glass-card">
        <h2 class="gradient-text">Start Your Transformation Journey</h2>
        <p>Partner with Kinevra to unlock the full potential of your SAP investments</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .about-hero {
    padding: 160px 0 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero-content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .feature-item {
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .feature-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .feature-item p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .approach-steps {
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .sidebar-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .sidebar-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .facts-list,
  .values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .facts-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .facts-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .values-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .values-list li::before {
    content: '‚Üí';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 60px 0 100px;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-content > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .content-sidebar {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-content {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
